com.extensia.xcp.services.restapi.model.service

Class CardRenderOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.extensia.xcp.services.restapi.model.service.CardRenderOption

  • public class CardRenderOption
extends java.lang.Object
    Class defining constants for configuring card image rendering options in the CardRequestService.serviceOptions map in card production requests. The card image rendering service generates and returns an image of the information printed on the front and/or back of the printed card.

        public static final java.lang.String CardSides

      • ImageRotation

        public static final java.lang.String ImageRotation
        Service parameter used to control the orientation of the rendered card image. Supported image rotation values are NoRotation, Clockwise90, Clockwise180 and Clockwise270. The default setting is NoRotation.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ImageQuality

        public static final java.lang.String ImageQuality
        Service parameter used to configure the image quality setting of the rendering process. The value must be a valid floating point number between "0.0" and "1.0". The default setting is "0.8".
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • RenderAndPrint

        public static final java.lang.String RenderAndPrint
        OutputMode value that configures the service to render the card image and print a physical card. The card image is returned once the card printing process has completed.

      • RenderOnly

        public static final java.lang.String RenderOnly
